The project "Online Boutique" has been developed by https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/microservices-demo

Modifications made by the University of Stuttgart:

- Project: Initialized the project by copying the original `src`
- Frontend, Checkout, Recommendation: use TLS for gRPC depending on env variables (requires base image with root certificates)
- Frontend, Checkout, Payment: mock optional and premium feature
- Frontend: add "OS Medium", "OS Large", and "Kuberenets" as platforms
- Cart: added MySQL support following https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/microservices-demo/pull/1836/files extended by the creation of the database table inside the code and the conditional use of SSL
- Analytical: added "Analytical Service" by copying "Recommendation" and adpating it
- Loadgenerator: added TLS support